ns out the business of boo is surprisingly complicated. Time magazine's <a href=\"http://entertainment.time.com/author/rothmanlily/\" target=\"_blank\">Lily Rothman</a> has <a href=\"http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,2155000,00.html\" target=\"_blank\">penned a story</a> for the latest issue of the magazine called <a href=\"http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,2155000,00.html?pcd=pw-edit\" target=\"_blank\">\"Monsters Inc: Inside the weird world of professional haunting.\"</a> She says haunted houses have had to up the ante to get a gasp these days, including one in Pennsylvania:</p>\n<p>\"The idea was to get that adrenaline rush for people who have been to a lot of haunted houses -- you would have the option to go through the haunted house naked.\"</p>\n<p><object id=\"flashObj\" classid=\"clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=9,0,47,0\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://c.brightcove.com/services/viewer/federated_f9?isVid=1&amp;isUI=1\" />\n<param name=\"bgcolor\" value=\"#FFFFFF\" />\n<param name=\"flashVars\" value=\"videoId=2750989650001&amp;linkBaseURL=http%3A%2F%2Fentertainment.time.com%2F2013%2F10%2F21%2Fbehind-the-scenes-how-a-haunted-house-scares-up-screams%2F&amp;playerID=1917933886001&amp;playerKey=AQ~~,AAAAABGEUMg~,hNlIXLTZFZn-NQOazMchMDWH0SI1hX7f&amp;domain=embed&amp;dynamicStreaming=true\" />\n<param name=\"base\" value=\"http://admin.brightcove.com\" />\n<param name=\"seamlesstabbing\" value=\"false\" />\n<param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" />\n<param name=\"swLiveConnect\" value=\"true\" />\n<param name=\"allowScriptAccess\" value=\"always\" />\n<embed src=\"http://c.brightcove.com/services/viewer/federated_f9?isVid=1&amp;isUI=1\" flashvars=\"videoId=2750989650001&amp;linkBaseURL=http%3A%2F%2Fentertainment.time.com%2F2013%2F10%2F21%2Fbehind-the-scenes-how-a-haunted-house-scares-up-screams%2F&amp;playerID=19179